Sometimes you may want to just pack your bags and head to somewhere amazing. With the high paced lifestyles many of us live, being inspired by some quotes will help us look forward to planning a trip when time permits. You may have just arrived back from a stunning break over the weekend? Or you may yearn for a getaway away from life’s pressures? If this you, then why not be inspired to travel with these travel quotes. Remember, life is too short not to go out and explore. "One way to get the most out of life is to look upon it as an adventure." - William Feather. "You don't have to be rich to travel well." - Eugene Fodor. “Once a year, go someplace you've never been before.” – The Dalai Lama. "A good traveler has no fixed plans, and it not intent on arriving"- Lao Tsu. Traveling - it leaves you speechless, then turns you into a storyteller.